This installer downloads a ZIP file from a Git repository and extracts it into a folder of your choice.

HOW TO RUN THE INSTALLER

1. Open PowerShell.
2. Navigate to the folder containing the installer:
   cd "path\to\folder"
3. Allow script execution for this session:
   Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
4. Run the installer:
   .\Install.ps1
5. To specify a custom installation path:
   .\Install.ps1 -InstallPath "C:\YourFolder"

UNINSTALLING

To remove the installed files, run:
   .\Uninstall.ps1
